      "releaseNotes": "This update of Noir brings another set of website fixes and improvements, mostly based on your website reports, so thanks so much for submitting those!\n\nIf you enjoy using Noir and want to support its development, please consider leaving a review in the App Store. It really helps a lot and I'd truly appreciate it a ton!\n\nJeffrey",
